PrecisReappointment of WILLIAM M. MURPHY, of Liverpool, Nova Scotia, as a Canadian representative to the General Council of the Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years; and as a Canadian representative to the Fisheries Commission of the Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective June 21, 1996.
